[05/06/2018 04:53:38] <font color="#ffffff">Sí.</font>
[05/06/2018 04:53:40] <font color="#ffffff">Oh, míralo.</font>
[05/06/2018 04:53:41] <font color="#ffffff">Oh, vaya...</font>
